description: To investigate the RNA binding proteins that change following mTOR inhibition, HeLa cells were treated with and without 200nM Torin1 for an hour. Cells were the UV254 cross-linked, lysed and large scale  whole cell oligo(dT) based pulldowns were performed with identification and quantification of purified proteins by label free mass spectrometry.
